---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold">About APG Patterns Examples</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg">
        Accessible UI component implementations across React, Vue, Svelte, and Astro following
        WAI-ARIA APG patterns
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
      <div class="text-muted-foreground space-y-4">
        <p>
          This project provides accessible UI components and test cases that follow the
          <a
            href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            WAI-ARIA Authoring Practices Guide (APG)
          </a>
          patterns.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each component is implemented across four major frontend frameworks: <strong>React</strong
          >, <strong>Vue</strong>, <strong>Svelte</strong>, and <strong>Astro</strong> (Web Components),
          providing familiar implementation examples to help you learn about accessibility and WAI-ARIA.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each component includes tests to verify APG pattern compliance, which you can use directly
          to ensure accessibility of your own components. The test documentation is also designed in
          an AI-friendly format, making it easy to generate test cases.
        </p>
        <p>
          Additionally, we provide styling that supports dark mode, high contrast mode, and forced
          colors mode to further assist in developing accessible components.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Pattern Coverage</h2>
      <div class="text-muted-foreground space-y-4">
        <p>
          This project provides implementations for <strong>all 30 patterns</strong> defined in the
          <a
            href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/patterns/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            WAI-ARIA APG
          </a>, plus 2 additional patterns (Toggle Button and Data Grid) â€” <strong
            >32 patterns in total</strong
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each pattern is implemented across all four frameworks: <strong>React</strong>, <strong
            >Vue</strong
          >, <strong>Svelte</strong>, and <strong>Astro</strong> (Web Components).
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Styling</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted-foreground list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
        <li>High contrast mode support</li>
        <li>Reduced motion preferences support</li>
        <li>Forced colors mode support</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Contributing</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
        We welcome contributions! Please see our
        <a
          href="https://github.com/masuP9/apg-patterns-examples/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-primary hover:underline"
        >
          Contributing Guide
        </a>
        for details.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">Links</h2>
      <ul class="text-muted-foreground list-inside list-disc space-y-2">
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            WAI-ARIA Authoring Practices Guide
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/masuP9/apg-patterns-examples"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            GitHub Repository
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/masuP9/apg-patterns-examples/issues"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            Issue Tracker
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/masuP9/apg-patterns-examples/discussions"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-primary hover:underline"
          >
            Discussions
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
